---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Anaesthetics — Examinations" description="ANZCA Primary Exam (PEx) and Final Exam (FEx) structure, requirements, and dates.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Examinations</h1>
    <p>Anaesthetics — ANZCA · Both exams run twice yearly</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Primary Exam (PEx)</h2>
    <p>Taken during Basic Training. Covers applied physiology, pharmacology, anatomy, measurement, equipment, quality and safety.</p>

    <h3>Written Component</h3>
    <table class="level-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>Format</th><th>Duration</th><th>Weight</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>MCQ</td><td>150 questions</td><td>150 min</td><td>Pass/fail gate</td></tr>
        <tr><td>SAQ</td><td>15 questions</td><td>150 min</td><td>50% of final mark</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Oral Component</h3>
    <table class="level-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>Format</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Vivas</td><td>3 vivas</td><td>20 min each</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Passing Requirements</h3>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Must pass MCQ section (gate)</li>
      <li>Must score at least 40% on SAQs to advance to vivas</li>
      <li>Overall: minimum 50% combined score from SAQs and vivas</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Final Exam (FEx)</h2>
    <p>Taken during Advanced Training. Assesses final formal competence and knowledge across all areas.</p>

    <h3>Written Component</h3>
    <table class="level-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>Format</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>MCQ</td><td>150 questions</td><td>150 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>SAQ</td><td>15 questions</td><td>150 min</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Oral Component</h3>
    <table class="level-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>Format</th><th>Duration</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Medical vivas</td><td>2 vivas</td><td>15 min each</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Anaesthesia vivas</td><td>8 vivas (over 3 days)</td><td>15 min each</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Passing Requirements</h3>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>40%+ on both MCQ and SAQ to reach viva stages</li>
      <li>50% overall score</li>
      <li>Pass anaesthesia vivas</li>
      <li>Pass at least one additional section</li>
      <li>Score 5+ on four of eight anaesthesia vivas</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Exam Dates</h2>
    <p>Both exams run twice yearly — <strong>2026.1</strong> and <strong>2026.2</strong> cycles. Multiple venues across Australia and Aotearoa New Zealand.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
